{"tid":890569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(迫爆東涌) 陳帆：人流依然暢順、有秩序","createTime":"2018-11-05T11:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T02:47:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29429d98636bf5a9cbff113827404bd68c3ec19c","tid":890569,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T11:54:54.000Z","msg":"運房局局長陳帆指，昨日通過港珠澳大橋香港聯檢大樓出入境者共達十萬人次，調動穿梭巴士亦達二千班次，整體交通、人流仍是相對暢順、有秩序，問題是如何平衡東涌居民的起居生活和輪候B6接駁巴士者的安全，稱政府已密切留意情況，採取必要安排措施，減少對東涌居民的影響。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有否預計到東涌出現的混亂，陳帆指，規劃港珠澳大橋刻意減少車流量，其中一個考慮是要照顧東涌居民的起居生活，同時確保往返機場道路暢順。<br />\n<br />\n至於有意見要求遷移現位於東涌的B6車站，陳帆稱，政府需要考慮此舉會否令從港鐵站上地面候車的乘客會否構成不便，以及新站有否足夠地方給乘客排隊，稱會繼續跟進。他又稱，現在政府優先要處理，是如何讓人流分散，不會只集中於某點，並做到有秩序管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/5153-d20181105-8267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F5153-d20181105-8267&d=PjAGIXuhr%2FYv5tc13vOj9%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=0a81168a\" target=\"_blank\">http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/5153-d20181105-8267</a>"},{"pid":"6a5307a0588c9e5c1fa9514a8a47f77222f2e08a","tid":890569,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb8c344562476619061af612fcec501b12d96bd","tid":890569,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a9527951c68c1ad01efd5a94c1e7dc8e4a3ed4","tid":890569,"uid":187180,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">陳帆仆你個街我屌你老母！！！！！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal